h1. Open Source Anchor Project (OSAP) Wiki

As active sailors, and especially cruisers, one of the most important and most hotly debated items are anchors.  The purpose of this project is to develop a low cost, open source anchor that is readily crafted from globally available materials with readily available techniques.

